&gt; On Mon, 19 Jan 2026 at 23:49, Daniel Herr &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="cfabaea1a6aaa3a7aabdbdbca0a9bbb8e1e1e18fa8a2aea6a3e1aca0a2"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
