&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://developers.google.com/privacy-sandbox/relevance/setup/web/chrome-facilitated-testing"&gt;https://developers.google.com/privacy-sandbox/relevance/setup/web/chrome-facilitated-testing&lt;/a&gt;&gt;for three more milestones.
