&gt;&gt; On Fri, Dec 19, 2025 at 2:52 PM Reilly Grant &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="0e7c6b67622020204e6d667c6163677b6320617c69"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
