This feature was launched on Desktop in Chrome 136 and Android in 142, and
we unfortunately forgot to request Intent to Ship approvals. I just
realized this mistake while we were cleaning up old feature flags, my
apologies. Are there any concerns or could we please have retroactive LGTMs?&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

For context, this was an additional feature to WebAuthn that had an already
existing spec and an implementation in WebKit. Several large Relying
Parties have adopted it already.

