&gt;&gt;&gt; *Web developers*: No signals
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Presumably, we're shipping this because this is something developers
&gt;&gt;&gt; want to use..
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Yes, authors need this. Not only for Scroll-Driven Animations, but also
