On Wed, Oct 22, 2025 at 9:46 PM 'Philipp Hancke' via blink-dev &lt;
&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7517191c1b1e5811100335161d071a181c00185b1a0712"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:

&gt; This makes a lot of sense but why did this end up as `.metadata()` when
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://w3c.github.io/webrtc-encoded-transform/#dom-rtcencodedvideoframe-getmetadata"&gt;https://w3c.github.io/webrtc-encoded-transform/#dom-rtcencodedvideoframe-getmetadata&lt;/a&gt;
